Itemized Passive Description:
*As the 2nd or 3rd attacker in a turn at the start of turn*
- Changes Ki Spheres: AGL to TEQ
*Per "Future Saga" Category ally on the team*
- ATK & DEF 40%{passiveImg:up_g} (up to 200%)
- All enemies' ATK & DEF 8%{passiveImg:down_y} (no more than -40%)
*Per "Future Saga" Category ally whose name includes
"Clone" on the team*
- ATK & DEF 20%{passiveImg:up_g} (up to 100%)
- All enemies' ATK & DEF 6%{passiveImg:down_y} (no more than -30%)
*When the team includes all five Extreme Types*
- ATK & DEF 150%{passiveImg:up_g}
- Interrupts the attacked enemy
*1 or more TEQ Ki Spheres obtained*
- Damage reduction rate 40%{passiveImg:up_g} when receiving an attack
from an enemy who is hit by the character's Super Attack
*When attacking with 12 or more Ki*
- ATK & DEF 200%{passiveImg:up_g}
- ATK & DEF 200%{passiveImg:up_g} when the target enemy is in the
following status: HP is 60% or less, {passiveImg:atk_down}, {passiveImg:def_down},
{passiveImg:stun} or {passiveImg:astute}
